---
import Stars from '../ui/Stars.astro';
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
---

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">
      Real Results From Real Clients
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      See what clients say about working with Rebel Ape.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Website design is premium quality. Adam is truly attentive to our needs. He was there when we needed him in an emergency. I cannot say enough about this team!
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Lori <span class="font-bold">M.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        I've used Rebel Ape's website design for years and their work has been excellent. They respond quickly to requests and recently delivered a redesign that puts all important information up front, preventing visitors from having to search. Highly recommend. *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Pete <span class="font-bold">T.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        I was pressed for time and needed a website live ASAP. Adam secured my domain, designed my site, handled all content, and got it live quickly. Thorough, quality work with great attention to detail. *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        John <span class="font-bold">G.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 4 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        I needed items added to my website and Rebel Ape did it fast and beautifully at a price I could afford. They saved me valuable time while delivering excellent quality work. *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Glory <span class="font-bold">S.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 5 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Adam and the Rebel Ape crew were instrumental in getting our project off the ground with logo design and website work. They went above and beyond in every respect and provided far more than we expected. *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        William <span class="font-bold">R.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 6 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Adam was great to work with on our website. Very prompt, professional, and projects were completed on time. Excellent service and quality work throughout. *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Loretta <span class="font-bold">S.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <div class="mt-16 text-center">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      Ready to see your website perform beautifully? Let's get started on your next project.
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <Button text="Schedule a Call" icon="phone" href="https://schedule.therebelape.com" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>